manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Star Wars Mission Fleet Blast off into galactic action and adventure with the Star Wars Mission Fleet figures and vehicles! These fun figures and vehicles allow kids to imagine action-packed battles between the dark side and the light side of the Force. Star Wars Mission Fleet toys are kid-friendly and make a great introduction to the Galaxy of Star Wars for boys and girls ages 4 and up! (Additional products each sold separately. Subject to availability.) May the Force be with you!

Clone Commando Clash Galactic action and adventure await with the Star Wars Mission Clone Commando Clash 4-figure collection! Kids can pretend to charge into battle on mercenary missions in the wake of the Clone Wars with the members of the Bad Batch! Imagine bold adventures with Hunter (Bad Batch), Echo (Bad Batch), Wrecker (Bad Batch), and Crosshair (Imperial) figures! The entertainment-inspired Star Wars details and 2.5-inch-scale make this action figure 4-pack an awesome addition to any Star Wars collection. Star Wars: The Bad Batch Series-Inspired Design and Detail Imagine setting off on daring missions with the Bad Batch’s Hunter, Echo, Wrecker, and Crosshair! The 2.5-inch-scale Clone Commando Clash action figure 4-pack comes with 10 detachable entertainment-inspired accessories, so boys and girls can imagine action-packed battles from the Star Wars Galaxy! Includes Hunter (Bad Batch), Echo (Bad Batch), Wrecker (Bad Batch), and Crosshair (Imperial) figures, featuring multiple points of articulation and design and detail inspired by the Star Wars: The Bad Batch animated series. Star Wars: The Bad Batch They call themselves the Bad Batch, but the motley crew that makes up Clone Force 99 boasts an astounding 100 percent success rate and skills unseen in any other Clone Troopers. Adept at working together, Hunter, Wrecker, Tech, and Crosshair use their unique talents and specialized physiology to execute extraordinary solutions on the battlefield. And after rescuing the Clone Trooper Echo from Separatist captivity, they welcome the cybernetic soldier into their fold.
